# ==============================================================================
# .gitignore — Mohamed Nana academic website
# Only the docs/ folder (the deployed site) is tracked.
# Everything else is local working material.
# ==============================================================================

# ── Ignore everything by default ──────────────────────────────────────────────
*

# ── Re-allow the files/folders git should track ───────────────────────────────
!.gitignore
!CLAUDE.md
!README.md
!MEMORY.md

# docs/ — the GitHub Pages site (the only thing that deploys)
!docs/
!docs/**

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
